OL,3,CKhalife guilty of spying for Iran: How
OL,4,Cteen turned into 'slapstick' James Bond
OL,6,FThe soldier turned spy - how Daniel
OL,7,FKhalife went from being in the British
OL,8,FArmy to supplying Iran with secret
OL,9,Finformation and escaping prison, as
OL,10,FITV News' Sam Holder reports
OL,12,FWords by Rachel Dixon and Sam Holder
OL,14,FDaniel Khalife has been found guilty
OL,15,Fof spying for Iran but was cleared of
OL,16,Fcarrying out a bomb hoax, at Woolwich
OL,17,FCrown Court.
OL,19,FHe claimed he was a double agent and
OL,20,Fwas helping the UK by supplying Iran
OL,21,Fwith information.
