OL,3,CKhalife guilty of spying for Iran: How
OL,4,Cteen turned into 'slapstick' James Bond
OL,6,FBut on Thursday morning the jury
OL,7,Fconvicted Khalife of breaching the
OL,8,FOfficial Secrets Act and Terrorism
OL,9,FAct, after 23 hours of deliberation.
OL,11,FHe was emotionless in the dock as he
OL,12,Fwas acquitted of perpetrating a bomb
OL,13,Fhoax.
OL,15,FThe 23-year-old of Kingston hit the
OL,16,Fheadlines after fleeing Wandsworth
OL,17,Fprison, by tying himself to a food
OL,18,Ftruck in September 2023, leading to a
OL,19,Fthree day man hunt taking place.
