OL,3,CKhalife guilty of spying for Iran: How
OL,4,Cteen turned into 'slapstick' James Bond
OL,6,FBut his Iranian spy plot began far
OL,7,Fearlier than his now infamous jail-
OL,8,Fbreak.
OL,10,FSoldier turned spy
OL,12,FAt just 16-years-old, Khalife joined
OL,13,Fthe British army in 2018 and was
OL,14,Fstationed at Stafford Barracks with
OL,15,Fthe Royal Corps of Signals.
OL,17,FWithin a year, he'd reached out to
OL,18,FIranian officials through a Facebook
OL,19,Fmessage, telling them he would stay
OL,20,Fundercover in the British Army for "25-
OL,21,Fplus years" for them.
