OL,6,FPolice later went on to find over 700
OL,7,Fphotos of military equipment on his
OL,8,Fdevices and a spreadsheet with the
OL,9,Fnames of army personnel.
OL,11,FHe even claimed his Iranian handlers
OL,12,Fhid a bundle of cash in a doggy bag in
OL,13,Fa North London park.
OL,15,FKhalife was meant to visit his
OL,16,Fhandlers in Tehran but only made it to
OL,17,FIstanbul as he claims he got too
OL,18,Fscared.
