OL,3,CKhalife guilty of spying for Iran: How
OL,4,Cteen turned into 'slapstick' James Bond
OL,6,FKhalife claimed he was helping Britain
OL,7,Fby feeding Iran false information.
OL,9,FBut Khalife ended up endangering the
OL,10,Flife of Nazanin Zaghari Ratcliffe by
OL,11,Fsending a fake document to Iran which
OL,12,Fsaid the British government was not
OL,13,Fwilling to negotiate over her release.
OL,15,FHe would not have been caught, but was
OL,16,Finstead arrested after he approached
OL,17,FBritish intelligence services offering
OL,18,Fto be a double agent.
