OL,6,FIf Khalife had not contacted MI5 to
OL,7,Ftell them about his contact with Iran,
OL,8,Fneither they nor the police would ever
OL,9,Fhave known, his barrister told the
OL,10,Fcourt.
OL,12,FKhalife told jurors he wanted to prove
OL,13,Fbosses wrong after being told his
OL,14,FIranian heritage could stop him
OL,15,Fworking in military intelligence, and
OL,16,Fcame up with his elaborate double
OL,17,Fagent plot after watching the TV spy
OL,18,Fthriller Homeland.
