OL,6,FGul Nawaz Hussain KC, defending, said
OL,7,Fthe double agent plot was "hapless"
OL,8,Fand "sometimes bordering on the
OL,9,Fslapstick", more "Scooby-Doo" than
OL,10,FJames Bond.
OL,12,FPrison break
OL,14,FDuring his time in Wandsworth prison,
OL,15,Fpolice said Khalife had an uncanny
OL,16,Fability to manipulate others - and
OL,17,Fmanaged to get a job in its kitchen
OL,18,Fwhich he shouldn't have been able to.
