OL,6,FHis actions could have put military
OL,7,Fpersonnel's lives at risk and
OL,8,F"prejudiced" the UK's national
OL,9,Fsecurity, the Crown Prosecution
OL,10,FService (CPS) said.
OL,12,FBethan David, from the CPS, said: "As
OL,13,Fa serving soldier of the British Army
OL,14,FDaniel Khalife was employed and
OL,15,Fentrusted to uphold and protect the
OL,16,Fnational security of this country.
OL,17,FBut, for purposes of his own, Daniel
OL,18,FKhalife used his employment to
OL,19,Fundermine national security.
