OL,9,Fpiece together and demonstrate that
OL,10,FKhalife had gathered and shared much
OL,11,Fof this classified information,
OL,12,Faccepted hundreds of pounds for his
OL,13,Fefforts and even travelled to Turkey
OL,14,Fas part of his unlawful conduct.
